&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;赤い空パノラマ&lt;/div&gt;
    今晩のHermosa Beach の美しい雲。このパノラマでは右側にMalibu が見えています。 
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><category term="Dusk" /><category term="Panoramas" /><summary type="html">Clouds did not disappoint this evening in Hermosa Beach. In this panorama you can also see Malibu on the right side. 赤い空パノラマ 今晩のHermosa Beach の美しい雲。このパノラマでは右側にMalibu が見えています。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04179-HDR-Pano.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R04179-HDR-Pano.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Foggy Marina</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220106/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Foggy Marina" /><published>2022-01-06T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-06T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/marina</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220106/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
   Went to Marina del Rey for the sunset, but there was heavy fog when we got there. The opposite bank completely disappeared.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;霧のマリーナ&lt;/div&gt;
   夕日を見にマリーナ・デル・レイに行ったのですが、霧が濃くて。対岸が全く見えなくなってしまった。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Marina del Rey" /><category term="Fog" /><category term="Black and White" /><category term="Water" /><category term="Harbors" /><summary type="html">Went to Marina del Rey for the sunset, but there was heavy fog when we got there. The opposite bank completely disappeared. 霧のマリーナ 夕日を見にマリーナ・デル・レイに行ったのですが、霧が濃くて。対岸が全く見えなくなってしまった。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0123.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0123.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Pelican Cove</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220105/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pelican Cove" /><published>2022-01-05T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-05T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pelican-cove</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220105/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
   Sunset at Pelican Cove in Rancho Palos Verdes. The Point Vicente Lighthouse is in the distance, at right.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ペリカン・コーブ&lt;/div&gt;
   ランチョ・パロス・バーデスのペリカン・コーブでの夕日。右手遠くに見えるのはポイントビセンテ灯台。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Palos Verdes" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Pacific Ocean" /><summary type="html">Sunset at Pelican Cove in Rancho Palos Verdes. The Point Vicente Lighthouse is in the distance, at right. ペリカン・コーブ ランチョ・パロス・バーデスのペリカン・コーブでの夕日。右手遠くに見えるのはポイントビセンテ灯台。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R03994-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R03994-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hermosa Beach</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220104/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hermosa Beach" /><published>2022-01-04T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-04T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hermosa</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220104/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
Very small surf in Hermosa Beach, looking north to Manhattan Beach.   Kind of a companion to the &lt;a href=&quot;/220103/&quot;/&gt;previous photo&lt;/a&gt;, but the light was more diffused today.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ハーモサ・ビーチ&lt;/div&gt;
   ハーモサビーチの小さな波、北のマンハッタンビーチ方面を眺める。&lt;a href=&quot;/220103/&quot;/&gt;前の写真&lt;/a&gt;と大体同じですが、今日は光が拡散していました。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Very small surf in Hermosa Beach, looking north to Manhattan Beach. Kind of a companion to the previous photo, but the light was more diffused today. ハーモサ・ビーチ ハーモサビーチの小さな波、北のマンハッタンビーチ方面を眺める。前の写真と大体同じですが、今日は光が拡散していました。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0070.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0070.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Redondo Riviera</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220103/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Redondo Riviera" /><published>2022-01-03T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-03T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/riviera</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220103/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Looking towards Hermosa Beach, LA and Malibu, from Avenue C in Redondo Beach.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;レドンドのリヴィエラ&lt;/div&gt;
   レドンドビーチのアベニューC道からハーモサビーチ、ロサンゼルスとマリブ方面を見る。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Redondo Beach" /><category term="Beach" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Looking towards Hermosa Beach, LA and Malibu, from Avenue C in Redondo Beach. レドンドのリヴィエラ レドンドビーチのアベニューC道からハーモサビーチ、ロサンゼルスとマリブ方面を見る。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0036.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_IMG_0036.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Reflecting on the New Year</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220101/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Reflecting on the New Year" /><published>2022-01-01T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2022-01-01T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/pier-reflection</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/220101/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
The Hermosa Beach Pier reflects on the wet sand at sunset.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;新年を振り返って&lt;/div&gt;
 夕暮れ時、濡れた砂に映えるハーモサビーチピア。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hermosa Beach" /><category term="Hermosa Pier" /><category term="Sunset" /><category term="Low Tide" /><summary type="html">The Hermosa Beach Pier reflects on the wet sand at sunset. 新年を振り返って 夕暮れ時、濡れた砂に映えるハーモサビーチピア。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R03863-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2022/2201_A7R03863-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Japan Map</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211231/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Japan Map" /><published>2021-12-31T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2021-12-31T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/map</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211231/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
 I was fortunate to be able to go all these places in Japan over the past four years.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;日本地図&lt;/div&gt;
  この4年間で、日本のあちこちに行くことができたのは、幸運だったと思います。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Japan" /><summary type="html">I was fortunate to be able to go all these places in Japan over the past four years. 日本地図 この4年間で、日本のあちこちに行くことができたのは、幸運だったと思います。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/Japanmap.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/Japanmap.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hollywood Sign</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211227/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hollywood Sign" /><published>2021-12-27T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2021-12-27T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/hollywood-sign</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211227/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  The Hollywood hills at golden hour.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;ハリウッド・サイン&lt;/div&gt;
  マジックアワーにハリウッドヒルズを眺める。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hollywood" /><category term="Views" /><category term="Golden Hour" /><summary type="html">The Hollywood hills at golden hour. ハリウッド・サイン マジックアワーにハリウッドヒルズを眺める。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2112_A7R03716-gpx.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2112_A7R03716-gpx.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Griffith Park Trails</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211226/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Griffith Park Trails" /><published>2021-12-26T00:00:00-08:00</published><updated>2021-12-26T00:00:00-08:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/griffith-park</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/211226/">&lt;p class=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
  Looking southwest towards Century City and the Pacific Ocean.
     I wonder how many times these trails have been used in Hollywood movies as a location for the American West or Middle East.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;jp&quot;&gt;    
&lt;div class=&quot;title_jp&quot;&gt;グリフィスパークのトレイル&lt;/div&gt;
グリフィスパークから南西にセンチュリーシティ、太平洋方面を眺める。
  アメリカ西部や中東のハリウッド映画のロケ地として何度使われたことだろう。
&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Hollywood" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html">Looking southwest towards Century City and the Pacific Ocean. I wonder how many times these trails have been used in Hollywood movies as a location for the American West or Middle East. グリフィスパークのトレイル グリフィスパークから南西にセンチュリーシティ、太平洋方面を眺める。 アメリカ西部や中東のハリウッド映画のロケ地として何度使われたことだろう。</summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2112_A7R03744-HDR.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2021/2112_A7R03744-HDR.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>